rComments: One of the best profs that I had during my undergraduate study at Ottawa U! If you have the chance I totally recommend anyone to take his class.
I would recommend this prof to anyone. I had little prior interest in his course but he inspired me the most. Looking for his other courses but could not find any. Hope he still with U of O.

He is a very interesting and extremely knowledgeable professor. He works in the biomedical field, and his experience and case studies he shows you are incredible. He does his best - but you must remember he works full time as well, so sometime he may be a little late to class. But honestly, he is one of the best profs I've ever had at uOttawa.
